     * Latest Tropical Storm and Hurricane Information
          + Pacific
               o Latest eastern Pacific tropical advisories and warnings
                 (NHC)
               o Latest central Pacific (including Hawaii) tropical
                 advisories and warnings (CPHC)
               o NRL Tropical information age (with tracks and satellite
                 images)
               o Coastal watches/warnings, strike probabilities, etc...
               o Various marine analyses and graphics
               o Eastern Pacific Satellite image from NRL Monterey
               o Latest Eastern Pacific satellite image with pressure
                 analysisc
               o Eastern Pacific Tropical Weather Discussion
               o Tropical Storm track plot for the Indian Ocean
          + Atlantic
               o Latest tropical advisories and warnings (NHC)
               o NRL Tropical information age (with tracks and satellite
                 images)
               o Coastal watches/warnings, strike probabilities, etc...
               o Various marine analyses and graphics
               o Latest Atlantic satellite image with pressure analyses
               o Atlantic Tropical Weather Discussion

